    "description": "The Duck Pond is a short idle and clicker game. Throw various types of food into your pond to attract different types of ducks that gives you various bonuses. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/b44ff89123b0519caaee402441142c21.poster.avif?t=1722016814\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/b44ff89123b0519caaee402441142c21.webm?t=1722016814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/b44ff89123b0519caaee402441142c21.mp4?t=1722016814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features an ending. There are many idle games that continue on forever, and that you can keep playing. We prefer a game that you can actually finish. Can you unlock the epic giga duck?!?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/e25a507b2a5a4ab203fefe734fad287a.avif?t=1722016814\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>The game features different types of ducks, that each give unique bonuses. You get to decide which ducks you want to buy for your pond. They will even move into a small hut if your pond starts getting overcrowded. Check out the duckopedia to find the latest info and bonuses of each duck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/99fbeb7d3ef543cc0b04e21d1dc98b51.avif?t=1722016814\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>The corporations have filled the pond with garbage. Clear it out so your ducks have a clean pond. A clean pond is imperative for your ducks to have the best the life and to thrive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/b422be269e3c102546c1f900f8fa52e7.poster.avif?t=1722016814\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/b422be269e3c102546c1f900f8fa52e7.webm?t=1722016814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067180/extras/b422be269e3c102546c1f900f8fa52e7.mp4?t=1722016814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
